{"tid":1502452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"早幾日黑警仲想扮有做野, 今日即刻打柒你地香港人","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T17:04:15.000Z","uid":125079,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"006a6eb7a3e169e24359055fff82d90793cedbd1","tid":1502452,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:22:27.000Z","msg":"早幾日元朗恐襲終於告暴動<br />\n黑警私醫院刑即刻拘捕<br />\n將軍澳斬人都至少肯拉人(雖然根本唔係佢地查出黎)<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街 今日即刻派畜龍防暴狗打人<br />\n<br />\n同黨鐵勾結<br />\n繼續射爆人眼 射過期tg<br />\n繼續係鏡頭前濫用私刑<br />\n鬧市民/記者曱甴垃圾, 交得少稅過佢地班狗<br />\n係公眾平台射tg<br />\n亂開槍射中市民心口同個頭<br />\n<br />\n想做戲就做全套啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地班前線狗又引唔到手, 把口又收唔到, EQ又低<br />\n<br />\n冇人再信你地班死黑警呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YOYDPWN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYOYDPWN.jpg&h=126db443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrbFiP8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrbFiP8.jpg&h=728bb634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBW2xaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBW2xaa.jpg&h=752d73fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b57a19547fa454f606cf3ad82f8a098ebd1b8376","tid":1502452,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/qBW2xaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBW2xaa.jpg&h=d139d8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條撚樣原來識中文"},{"pid":"940eced9dddceddde3f2efc73519d7bcbb5abdf3","tid":1502452,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:23:23.000Z","msg":"Trump仔開火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201064119dce03d5023b7127ee21fcaf6250bba7","tid":1502452,"uid":988